==[[Esperanto]]==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-am]]'' (correlative suffix of time)

===Correlative===
'''iam'''

# [[sometime]], [[ever]] (indeterminate correlative of time)
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''iam''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Iam''' ajn'' thus means ''[[anytime]]'' or ''[[whenever]]''

